H0.text: What is the title of the chief of a lifeboat crew. Helmsman

H1.text: What is the title of the chief of a lifeboat crew. Boatswain

H2.text: What is the title of the chief of a lifeboat crew. Navigator

H3.text: What is the title of the chief of a lifeboat crew. Cox'n

A4.text: The coxswain is the person in charge of a boat, particularly its navigation and steering.

A5.text: In the United States Coast Guard and United States Coast Guard Auxiliary, the coxswain is the person in charge of a small boat.
